        p.intro Welcome to the Owlypixel's guitar escape! When I was in high school, I was obsessed with guitar. During those times I took some classic guitar classes and to measure my progress recorded myself with my old tape recorder. Due to the fact that old analog tape is not a very reliable medium, I decided to digitize my old recordings. So, without further ado, let me take you on a journey to a land of old memories, constantly hurting fingers, jolly improvisation, strict discipline and remarkable power of music.    
